37
00:03:26,410 --> 00:03:27,250
Lan Che,

38
00:03:27,820 --> 00:03:28,710
I promise

39
00:03:29,180 --> 00:03:30,600
I won't lie to you anymore.

40
00:03:36,410 --> 00:03:37,810
Actually, it's not my idea

41
00:03:37,810 --> 00:03:39,190
