117
00:07:46,660 --> 00:07:47,600
Yes.

118
00:07:50,180 --> 00:07:51,020
My Lord,

119
00:07:51,060 --> 00:07:53,800
can I borrow it for a few days?

120
00:07:56,900 --> 00:07:57,920
Thanks, My Lord.

121
00:08:09,460 --> 00:08:13,980
(Lou's Mansion)

122
00:08:15,530 --> 00:08:16,890
Take a look.

123
00:08:16,890 --> 00:08:18,040
Sweet apples and oranges.

124
00:08:18,340 --> 00:08:20,020
Some crunchy and sweet apples?

125
00:08:20,020 --> 00:08:21,110
How much is this?

126
00:08:21,370 --> 00:08:22,210
Two wen for one.

127
00:08:33,570 --> 00:08:34,510
Do you want oranges?

128
00:08:41,020 --> 00:08:43,380
Fresh apples and oranges.

129
00:08:43,380 --> 00:08:44,560
Take a look.

130
00:08:45,130 --> 00:08:46,930
Freshly made cakes.

131
00:08:46,930 --> 00:08:48,770
Ten wen for one pack.
Would you like some?

132
00:08:48,770 --> 00:08:49,800
I'll take one.

133
00:08:52,100 --> 00:08:53,190
Here you are.

134
00:08:55,250 --> 00:08:56,090
Thanks.

135
00:09:03,610 --> 00:09:05,510
Do you like it? I'll buy it for you.

136
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:11,310
I don't like it.

137
00:09:18,900 --> 00:09:20,360
We're closed.

138
00:09:20,540 --> 00:09:21,750
Can you stop...?

139
00:09:31,130 --> 00:09:32,680
I've followed you all day

140
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:34,190
without having any water.

141
00:09:35,020 --> 00:09:35,860
Can you

142
00:09:36,340 --> 00:09:38,120
invite me in for a cup of tea?

143
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,570
(Huanxi Clinic)

144
00:09:39,570 --> 00:09:41,480
It's a clinic, not a tea house.

145
00:09:41,980 --> 00:09:42,820
Only medicine,

146
00:09:43,570 --> 00:09:44,410
no tea.

147
00:09:47,490 --> 00:09:48,510
Are you hungry?

148
00:09:49,020 --> 00:09:50,270
Do you want an apple?

149
00:09:54,370 --> 00:09:55,750
What's wrong with you?

150
00:09:57,340 --> 00:09:58,270
Lan Che.

151
00:09:59,220 --> 00:10:00,360
I'm so sorry.

152
00:10:02,050 --> 00:10:03,311
Please forgive me.

153
00:10:13,340 --> 00:10:14,680
I don't want your stuff.

154
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:16,310
Just leave me alone.

155
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:29,020
(Huanxi Clinic)

156
00:10:38,660 --> 00:10:39,610
Lan Che.

157
00:10:39,610 --> 00:10:40,450
What?

158
00:10:42,170 --> 00:10:43,010
Look.

159
00:10:43,610 --> 00:10:44,450
I just

160
00:10:44,570 --> 00:10:46,210
made your

161
00:10:46,210 --> 00:10:48,270
favorite hot pepper soup.

162
00:10:55,860 --> 00:10:57,000
Help!

163
00:10:59,220 --> 00:11:00,710
Drink it while it's hot, okay?

164
00:11:08,420 --> 00:11:09,500
Hey, Boss,

165
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:11,190
stop being angry. Here.

166
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:16,740
No.

167
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:24,650
Come on.

168
00:11:24,650 --> 00:11:25,900
You can't get angry

169
00:11:25,900 --> 00:11:27,650
with an empty stomach, right?

170
00:11:27,650 --> 00:11:28,490
Here.

171
00:11:39,780 --> 00:11:41,580
What kind of pepper soup is this?

172
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:44,440
No salt, no pepper. It's so bad.

173
00:11:48,980 --> 00:11:49,820
Lan Che.

174
00:11:58,220 --> 00:12:00,050
You helped Lou Mingye and Huanxi

175
00:12:00,050 --> 00:12:01,490
to lie to me.

176
00:12:01,490 --> 00:12:03,240
Don't think I'm not angry at you.

177
00:12:06,340 --> 00:12:07,310
I'm innocent.

178
00:12:07,980 --> 00:12:11,800
I didn't know at first,

179
00:12:12,130 --> 00:12:14,390
but then I had no choice.

180
00:12:14,780 --> 00:12:16,600
Since you're just an accomplice,

181
00:12:17,420 --> 00:12:18,830
I don't blame you this time.

182
00:12:19,100 --> 00:12:19,940
Okay?

183
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:30,010
♪Dreams vanish like clouds and smoke♪

184
00:12:30,690 --> 00:12:31,600
I wish

185
00:12:32,810 --> 00:12:34,560
we could grow up

186
00:12:35,170 --> 00:12:36,630
together.

187
00:12:39,860 --> 00:12:41,710
Why are you saying this?

188
00:12:44,370 --> 00:12:45,560
In that case,

189
00:12:46,130 --> 00:12:48,310
I'd know you earlier than he did.

190
00:12:49,170 --> 00:12:51,480
I'd keep you like a treasure

191
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,680
and give you everything I had.

192
00:12:56,980 --> 00:12:58,120
Li Mo...

193
00:12:58,980 --> 00:12:59,920
In that case,

194
00:13:00,220 --> 00:13:01,480
would you choose me?

195
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:08,250
♪Fear you're so far away
when I wake up♪

196
00:13:09,690 --> 00:13:10,630
To be honest,

197
00:13:12,250 --> 00:13:14,560
I didn't like Lou Mingye at first.

198
00:13:15,660 --> 00:13:17,390
I thought I was better at everything.

199
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:20,270
However,

200
00:13:21,300 --> 00:13:23,000
when I asked him a question...

201
00:13:25,490 --> 00:13:26,330
Lou Mingye!

202
00:13:28,730 --> 00:13:30,600
I'm doing this for Lan Che.

203
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:33,600
I owe you one.

204
00:13:35,370 --> 00:13:36,750
I have a question.

205
00:13:37,930 --> 00:13:39,000
If one day,

206
00:13:39,660 --> 00:13:41,240
only one of you could survive,

207
00:13:41,930 --> 00:13:43,360
would you sacrifice your life

208
00:13:43,860 --> 00:13:44,750
for her?

209
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:47,290
♪Your face♪

210
00:13:47,820 --> 00:13:49,520
♪I've witnessed the passage of time.♪

211
00:13:49,540 --> 00:13:51,000
I'd do anything I can

212
00:13:54,300 --> 00:13:55,830
to keep her alive.

213
00:13:55,830 --> 00:13:58,820
♪Stuck in the memories♪

214
00:14:01,370 --> 00:14:02,510
I thought

215
00:14:03,220 --> 00:14:05,950
he was just a heartless hypocrite.

216
00:14:08,370 --> 00:14:09,390
I was wrong.

217
00:14:11,100 --> 00:14:12,040
He...

218
00:14:17,220 --> 00:14:18,830
is a trustworthy man.

219
00:14:18,830 --> 00:14:24,760
♪Fear our love
can't stand the test of time♪

220
00:14:24,780 --> 00:14:25,680
Okay.

221
00:14:26,570 --> 00:14:27,750
It's getting late.

222
00:14:28,170 --> 00:14:29,040
I'm leaving.

223
00:14:31,460 --> 00:14:32,390
Li Mo.

224
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:40,890
♪Fear we'll never♪

225
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:43,360
Thanks.

226
00:14:48,100 --> 00:14:49,480
Don't say that.

227
00:14:55,980 --> 00:15:02,980
(Huanxi Clinic)

228
00:15:18,460 --> 00:15:19,410
I'm the stupidest man

229
00:15:19,410 --> 00:15:21,120
in this world.

230
00:15:37,930 --> 00:15:38,950
What's wrong with you?

231
00:15:40,610 --> 00:15:42,830
Master brought back some Resina Ferulae.

232
00:15:43,050 --> 00:15:44,160
It stinks.

233
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:47,920
Two patients ran away because of this.

234
00:15:49,930 --> 00:15:51,190
There's no smell.

235
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:52,560
No smell?

236
00:15:53,050 --> 00:15:54,870
Are you serious?

237
00:15:59,900 --> 00:16:01,190
I can't smell it.

238
00:16:03,250 --> 00:16:04,270
Guys,

239
00:16:04,490 --> 00:16:05,440
stop acting.

240
00:16:09,570 --> 00:16:11,460
You're acting.

241
00:16:11,460 --> 00:16:12,300
That's true.

242
00:16:12,490 --> 00:16:13,390
Lan Che.

243
00:16:14,370 --> 00:16:15,210
Lan Che?

244
00:16:16,250 --> 00:16:17,560
Get up. It's enough.

245
00:16:19,370 --> 00:16:20,210
Lan Che?

246
00:16:21,100 --> 00:16:22,630
Lan Che! Lan Che!

247
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:24,700
She really passed out.

248
00:16:26,610 --> 00:16:28,120
- Boss!
- Boss!

249
00:16:30,620 --> 00:16:34,060
(Huanxi Clinic)

250
00:16:50,100 --> 00:16:51,160
You're awake.

251
00:16:53,540 --> 00:16:54,480
Father!

252
00:17:01,420 --> 00:17:02,560
Are you

253
00:17:03,020 --> 00:17:04,390
uncomfortable?

254
00:17:06,130 --> 00:17:07,390
I miss you so much.

255
00:17:09,020 --> 00:17:10,680
I'm right here.

256
00:17:16,580 --> 00:17:18,200
You've grown up.

257
00:17:18,730 --> 00:17:20,800
Why do you still like crying?

258
00:17:21,820 --> 00:17:23,080
Just tired.

259
00:17:25,580 --> 00:17:27,510
If you're not feeling well,

260
00:17:28,250 --> 00:17:29,440
go to sleep.

261
00:17:31,090 --> 00:17:32,750
But if I fall asleep,

262
00:17:33,900 --> 00:17:35,270
you'll be gone.

263
00:17:36,700 --> 00:17:38,200
I'm not going anywhere,

264
00:17:38,370 --> 00:17:39,210
okay?

265
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:48,350
It's a deal.

266
00:17:49,580 --> 00:17:50,420
Okay.

267
00:17:51,540 --> 00:17:52,870
It's a deal.

268
00:18:01,300 --> 00:18:02,270
Sleep.

269
00:18:12,610 --> 00:18:13,470
Qingyao.

270
00:18:14,940 --> 00:18:16,230
It's all my fault.

271
00:18:16,970 --> 00:18:18,390
I'm so sorry.

272
00:18:26,130 --> 00:18:27,080
My Lord!

273
00:18:27,940 --> 00:18:29,700
