283
00:19:13,130 --> 00:19:14,320
Do I know you?

284
00:19:15,730 --> 00:19:16,990
Stop kidding.

285
00:19:17,300 --> 00:19:18,510
It's all my fault.

286
00:19:18,970 --> 00:19:20,300
From now on, I won't

287
00:19:20,300 --> 00:19:21,560
keep any secret from you.

288
00:19:24,060 --> 00:19:25,560
Who are you?

289
00:19:28,450 --> 00:19:30,300
Why don't you speak?

290
00:19:30,300 --> 00:19:31,320
Then I'm leaving.

291
00:19:31,970 --> 00:19:32,810
Wait.

292
00:19:39,940 --> 00:19:41,350
Don't you remember me?

293
00:19:51,940 --> 00:19:53,160
I'm Lou Mingye,

294
00:19:53,970 --> 00:19:54,920
and you're Lan Che,

295
00:19:55,820 --> 00:19:57,080
the woman I love.

296
00:19:58,900 --> 00:20:00,900
You have a bad temper

297
00:20:00,900 --> 00:20:01,960
